  .background-image-holder
    = image_pack_tag "media/src/images/speeding-highway-traffic.jpg", alt: "image", class: 'background-image'
section
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-sm-12
        .text-center
          h3.mb-5.type--uppercase Why Excide?
        p.lead.m32.pb32 At Excide, we ensure a smooth process for your exit transaction. For every exit scenario, you are needed to go through several rounds of negotiations and valuations for the business. Hence, Excide will accompany you through each decision you make and carry out the necessary procedures and maximising your cash out. We will also help you gather the appropriate team to ensure a smooth closure of your transaction.
